  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cryptographically secure RNG using crypto.getRandomValues()",
    "Anti-bruteforce guards (block keyboard walks, weak fragments, ambiguous chars)",
    "Phonetic Shield mode — pronounceable yet resistant passwords",
    "Entropy DNA visualization per character class",
    "Passphrase generator with EFF-curated 200-word list",
    "PIN generator with sequence and pattern blocking",
    "Real-time entropy bits and crack-time estimation",
    "100% client-side — zero telemetry, zero data collection",
    "Dark/light theme with localStorage persistence",
    "Ctrl+Enter keyboard shortcut for quick regeneration"
